 rays. We\nconclude by discussing possible strategies to empirically test our theoretical\nmodels.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 22 May 2013 15:58:44 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 5 Dec 2013 22:29:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-12-09"}
